<refsection role="introduction">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <code>p:replace</code> step replaces matching nodes in
its primary input with the top-level node(s) of the
<code>replacement</code> port's document.</para>
</refsection>

<refsection role="step-declaration">
<title>Step declaration</title>
<xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../../../../xmlcalabash/src/main/resources/com/xmlcalabash/library.xpl" xpointer="xpath(/*/*[@type='p:replace'])"/>
</refsection>

<refsection role="errors"><title>Errors</title><para>
<error code="C0023">It
is a <glossterm>dynamic error</glossterm> if that pattern matches
an attribute or a namespace nodes. </error>
</para>
